
1  Ore te nkintanapata o Laitoriani, nelotu oltung'ani le Nkai eing'uaa Yuda nelotu Betel. Neitashe apa Yeroboam tembata o lperere lo lasar apej enkorropil. 
2   Neishiraki ilo tung'ani le Nkai olperere lo lasar to rorei lo Laitoriani ejo, “Lo perere lo lasar, lo perere, nji ejo Olaitriani: ‘Ng'ura, keikini enkaji e Daudi enkayioni, naa keji enkarna enye Yosia, naa kepolos ninye te shumata iyie lelo apolosak loo wuejitin e shumata, lelo oopej enkorropil te shumata iyie, naa kepuoi aapejoo iloik loo ltung'ana te shumata iyie.’ ” 
3  Neishoru ninye olmonekie teina olong ake, ejo, “Olmonekie ele oiroro Olaitoriani; ejo, ‘Ng'ura kegili ele perere lo lasar aasulaki enkop, ore nena kuruon naatii enchumata enye nebukokini enkop.’ ”


4  Ore ake pee ening olaiguanani ina kiroroto o ltung'ani le Nkai, naishiraka ilo perere lo lasar te Betel, neitorio enkaina enye teilo perere lo lasar ajo, “Embung'a ninye.” Ore ina aina enye duoo naitorioyie aimbung'ie ninye, netoyu, ometaa meekure errinyo. 
5  Nedanya sii olperere lo lasar neibukori nkuruon teilo perere lo lasar, te risioroto eilo monekie oishorua ilo tung'ani le Nkai to rorei lo Laitoriani. 
6  Nejoki olaiguanani ilo tung'ani le Nkai, “Toomonokoki taata to Laitoriani Enkai ino, pee etum enkaina ai anyaaki atisidana.” Neomon ilo tung'ani le Nkai Olaitoriani, neitoki enkaina olaiguanani aishiu, netiu anaa duoo. 
7  Neitoki olaiguanani ajoki ilo tung'ani le Nkai, “Wou maape ang pee ilo ainos endaa, naaisho sii enkishoroto.”


8  Nejoki ilo tung'ani le Nkai olaiguanani, “Tenikincho ninye olpisiaai le nkaji ino, maairiamariyie nanu iyie. Nemainos nanu endaa aashu aok enkare tene wueji; 
9  amu ina apa aaitanapa ororei lo Laitoriani, ejo, ‘Minos endaa nimiok enkare, nimilo aim enkoitoi duoo niimua.’ ” 
10  Neaku eshomo ninye aim ae oitoi, neitu eibelekenya aim enkoitoi duoo naimua elotu Betel.

Oloiboni moruo le Betel


11  Netii apa oloiboni moruo Betel. Nepuonu ilayiok lenyena aaliki nena pooki naataasa oltung'ani le Nkai ina olong te Betel; o lelo rorei sii ootiaaka olaiguanani, neliki ninche papaai lenye. 
12  Nejoki papaai lenye ninche, “Kaa oitoi eima?” Neitodol ilayiok lenyena ninye ina oitoi naimua oltung'ani le Nkai oing'uaa Yuda. 
13  Nejoki ninye ilayiok lenyena, “Erotokoki osikiria,” Neirotoki ninche ninye osikiria, neked ninye. 
14  Nelo ninye asujaa ilo tung'ani le Nkai neinepu etonita te ntonata olchani, oji olmaloni; nejoki ninye, “Eiyie doi oltung'ani le Nkai oing'uaa Yuda?”

Nejoki ninye, “Ee nanu.” 
15  Neitoki ajoki ninye, “Wou maape ang pee ilo ainos endaa.” 
16  Nejo ninye, “Marrinyo nanu alo tenebo iyie, anaa alo ajing atua aji tenebo iyie; nemainos nanu endaa anaa aok enkare tenebo iyie tene wueji; 
17  amu aatiaka nanu ororei lo Laitoriani, ‘Minos endaa nimiok enkare teine, nimirrinyo aim enkoitoi duoo niimua.’ ”


18  Nejoki ninye ilo tung'ani le Nkai, “Ara sii nanu oloiboni le Nkai anaa iyie, naairorie nanu olmalaika to rorei lo Laitoriani, ejo, ‘Torrinyu ninye meeu tenebo iyie enkaji ino pee etum ainosa endaa neok enkare.’ ”


19  Kake eteleja apa ninye ninye. Neaku eshomo tenebo ninye neinos endaa te nkaji enye neok enkare. 
20  Ore etonita ninche te mesa, nelotu ororei lo Laitoriani enetii ilo oiboni apa otorrinyuo ninye ariku; 
21  neishiraki ninye ilo tung'ani le Nkai apa oing'uaa Yuda, ejo, “Nji ejo Olaitoriani, ‘Ore enkaraki neitu imbung ororei lo Laitoriani, neitu imbung nkitanapat Olaitoriani Enkai, kake itorrinyunye, 
22  ninya endaa niok enkare tene wueji, nikitiaaka apa ninye iyie “Minos endaa nimiok enkare.” Mepuoi aanukaa osesen lino te nkurare oo loo papaai lino.’ ”


23  Ore ake pee eidip ainosa endaa neokisho neirotoki osikiria ilo oiboni duoo otorrinyuo ariku. 
24  Ore eloito nenang'are olng'atuny ninye te nkoitoi near ninye metua. Nenang'akini osesen lenye enkoitoi, neitashe osikiria tembata enye; neitashe sii olng'atuny te mbata o sesen. 
25  Naa ng'ura! etogiroitie iltung'ana nedol osesen otanang'akaki e nkoitoi, neitashe olng'atuny te mbata. Nepuonu aaimaki teina anasa apa namanya ilo oiboni moruo.


26  Ore ake pee ening ilo oiboni apa otorrinyuo ninye te nkoitoi ina, nejo ninye, “Oltung'ani le Nkai ilo; leitu ening ororei lo Laitoriani; neaku eishooyie Olaitoriani meinosa olng'atuny, neinos olng'atuny ninye aar metua, terisioroto eilo rorei oirorie ninye.” 
27  Nejoki ninye ilayiok lenyena, “Erotokoki nanu esikiria” neaku eirotokoki ninye esikiria, 
28  Nelo ninye neinepu ninye eirrag te nkoitoi, neitashe osikiria o lng'atuny te mbata ilo sesen Neitu einos olng'atuny ilo sesen neitu eony ilo sikiria. 
29  Neya ilo oiboni osesen leilo tung'ani le Nkai neiteleiki osikiria, nerrinyu ayau enkanasa pee eishiraki nenukaa. 
30  Neirragie ilo sesen anukaa te nkurare enye makewan; neishiraki ninche ninye ejo, 
31  “Ee olalashe lai!” Ore ake pee eidip atunukai ninye, nejoki ilayiok lenyena, “Tenaye akenya, entunukayioki te nkurare natunukarieki oltung'ani le Nkai; erragie iloik laainei tembata oo loik lenyena. 
32  Amu ore ina kiroroto apa naishiraka to rorei lo Laitoriani olperere lo lasar te Betel, o nkajijik pooki oo wuejitin e shumata naati nkanas e Samaria, esipa, keyookini aaitabaya.”

Engoki torrono e Yeroboam


33  Ore te siadi ena eitu eibelekenya nkoitoi e Yeroboam torrok, kake enyaaka aitayu ilapolosak too wuejitin e shumata tiatua olorere pooki; te pooki ooyieu, neitisiny metaa ilapolosak too wuejitin e shumata. 
34  Neaku ena bae eng'oki te nkaji e Yeroboam, o metaa eiwuang'ieki neidaikieki aaishie te nkop.

